  "translations": {
    "en": "Uthman said: \"By Allah, if authority is given to me, I shall certainly send you back to your first Lord.\" When death came upon al-Miqdad, he said: \"Inform Uthman that I have indeed been returned to my Lord, the First and the Last.\"",
